# Metamodel repository — code ownership rules.
# See https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: metamodel architect reviews all changes
*                               @metamodel-architect

# Ontology source data — requires data owner + architect
data/                           @metamodel-architect @data-owner

# Relation catalog spec
docs/architecture/relation_catalog_v2_spec.yaml  @metamodel-architect

